      *              * Rilettura tabella con rilascio records al Sort  *
      *              * e determinazione presenza progressivi per cor-  *
      *              * rispettivi e aliquote per legenda               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-tai-snx-cor          .
           move      spaces               to   w-tai-snx-asc          .
           move      spaces               to   w-tai-snx-and          .
           move      spaces               to   w-tai-snx-asi          .
           move      zero                 to   w-tai-ctr-001          .
       stp-srt-inp-cs1-820.
           add       1                    to   w-tai-ctr-001          .
           if        w-tai-ctr-001        >    w-tai-num-ele
                     go to stp-srt-inp-cs1-999.
