           add       rf-mgi-ibl-iva
                    (w-tai-ctr-001)       to   w-tai-ibl-cor
                                              (w-tai-ctr-002)         .
           add       rf-mgi-imp-iva
                    (w-tai-ctr-001)       to   w-tai-imp-cor
                                              (w-tai-ctr-002)         .
           go to     stp-srt-inp-cs2-280.
